      "side": 1,
      "message": "Unfortunately, that doesn\u0027t work. build_overrides/angle.gni isn\u0027t included in all the places that need this variable, since ANGLE is moving away from build_overrides and toward the new .gn approach that Chrome infra team is recommending.\n\njmadill@ can give you some background here.",
