      "writtenOn": "2021-01-07T20:49:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You can also define skia_standalone \u003d true here and have ANGLE define skia_standalone \u003d false in ANGLE\u0027s .gn. I really don\u0027t care if ANGLE or Skia has to acknowledge the other one exists ^^",
